entries.title: AI Will Make (Has Made) the Internet Mediocre...
entries.description:
Artificial Intelligence has already taken over most of the internet sites you see on a daily basis. Nearly everything is algorithmically-generated content. This will get even worse and it will be harder to even get basic information online. To schizo-post, soon "they" will replace everyone you know with an AI that continually generates a stream of infotainment for you to passively consoom forever.
